{"tid":1611103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣中槍18歲中五男生情況轉為穩定 - 商業電台","createTime":"2019-10-02T01:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T02:53:09.000Z","uid":249945,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"db5e60804197fdb3b349f66336a4b93e7ae87d0f","tid":1611103,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:07:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdCL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=a0103eb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com</a> &rsaquo; newsdetail"},{"pid":"728981eed3305b28ff767c126eeab3f222443c8a","tid":1611103,"uid":22590,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:14:56.000Z","msg":"一名18歲中五男生昨日在荃灣衝突期間被警察槍傷，<span style=\"color: red;\">在手術後由危殆轉為穩定</span>。在傷者就讀的荃灣何傳耀紀念中學外，早上有超過一百名學生及校友，在校門外默站及靜坐聲援，亦有學生派發單張，並高叫口號，批評警察濫暴。校長謝潤明表示，昨日與兩位副校長去探望受傷學生，當時學生正手術，今日會再去探望。被問到警方昨日開槍是否合適，謝潤明說要再了解，現時首要是梳理學生情緒，稍後亦會與門外聲援的舊生對話。<br />\n<br />\n校方表示，已啟動危機處理小組，由教育心理學家、校內老師及社工，輔導情緒受困擾的學生，亦會全力支援受傷學生和他的家人，同時希望學生在參與公眾活動時注意安全、遠離危險。<br />\n<br />\n保祐中槍手足"},{"pid":"2ad64a221ba44cfef6c3a6fe8a272209e5cccc95","tid":1611103,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:17:25.000Z","msg":"今日12點半，黑西裝癱瘓全中環！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610862</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ys8JWVq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fys8JWVq.jpg&h=0a01ddc5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rt9QBVr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRt9QBVr.jpg&h=ac54da07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b877c4829edfe71e6a4d77346a3af9d3c75d5f09","tid":1611103,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:18:19.000Z","msg":"天佑香港"},{"pid":"f64b15505d201a2062284779ab376a8050640329",